game.name: Swimming Pro
game.description:
Becoming the biggest swimmer of the world is a dream of your life. And, for this reason, you gave many years in getting yourself trained in both in and off the water. Luckily, you managed to consider your name among the world’s best swimmers. So, you have got participated in the World Championship of Swimming. Wow! This is a moment of your life you have been waiting for long. Tight your waist and roll up your sleeves to compete the swimming champions from all across the world in this brand new swimming sports game – Swimming Pro!

You have the guts to challenge the world’s best swimmers and beat their time. All you need to do is to collect as much medals as you can to increase your energy. Make sure that you have enough medals to move forward to the podium of champions. Swimming Pro is a free online HTML5 sports game designed to boys and girls from different age groups. Choose the country for which you want to play your swimmer and get him ready to race your player in the 100 M, 200 M or 400 M freestyle. 

It requires you to mark your victory in regional, national and international competitions in order to build your glorious athletic records. This will definitely help you to win the gold medals in the world’s best swimming championship and become a superstar in the pool. Play this cool funny sports game and get a chance to perform various locations around the world. Train yourself to achieve the optimum possible outcomes! Controls: Mouse to navigate, LMB to select, arrow keys left and right to pedal/swim faster and space to turn. Do you think that you have the talent to horde the maximum possible medals?
